OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening with rain
OL,7,Fslowly spreading east, Rain turning to
OL,8,Fsnow on the hills before clearing
OL,9,Fovernight, which may allow some frost
OL,10,Fto develop.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cold and quite cloudy start
OL,13,Fwith perhaps the odd spot of rain over
OL,14,FFife. Otherwise dry with increasingly
OL,15,Fbright or sunny spells, but feeling
OL,16,Fcooler than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
